#. +> trunk5
#: ../../user_manual/ekos.rst:5
msgid "**Ekos** is an advanced cross-platform (Windows®, Mac® OS, Linux®) observatory control and automation tool with a particular focus on Astrophotography. It is based on a modular extensible framework to perform common astrophotography tasks.  This includes highly accurate GOTOs using astrometry solver, ability to measure *and* correct polar alignment errors, auto-focus & auto-guide capabilities, and capture of single or stack of images with filter wheel support. Ekos is shipped with KStars."
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../user_manual/ekos.rst:10
msgid "Ekos introductory video"
msgstr ""

